snippet: The five-time world champion ski jumper Janne Ahonen of Finland will come out of retirement for a second time, aiming for the 2014 Winter Olympics in Sochi, Russia.
lead_paragraph: The five-time world champion ski jumper Janne Ahonen of Finland will come out of retirement for a second time, aiming for the 2014 Winter Olympics in Sochi, Russia.

headline.seo: Ski Jumper Janne Ahonen of Finland to Come Out of Retirement
headline.main: Former Ski Jumper Coming Out of Retirement
